      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUGLE GIRL (6) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (17.63) at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Can find winning form. OCCULENT (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.52) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park. Has a good record at this journey. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Has ability and can atone. SASSY SUPREME (7) was out of in the placings when eighth last time but prior to that clocked a dazzling 29.96 win over 525m at this track. Expected to feature on best figures. GEORGE JUDY (2) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
